    "description": "Traulsen commercial refrigeration service across Los Angeles — G-series reach-ins, RHT/RLT half-door, TBC/TBF blast chillers + freezers, undercounter spec-grade. INTELA-TRAUL microprocessor specialists. ITW Food Equipment family.",
